720258f-a.title: Manhattan: Greenwich Street - 11th Street (West)
720258f-a.text:
Greenwich Street, north from West 11th Street, showing
conditions prior to track removal (surface) by the '.P.A.
Incidently, the overhead eleveted line (9th Ave. line)
